  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::RevManager.NewsEventData
  Headline: 43 Students Disappeared in Protest Crackdowns
  Body: The Machine has grown even more openly vicious and cruel. The youth of our
    country, our future, are being suppressed and killed for daring to speak up for
    their fellow citizens. If we do not advocate for them they will be forgotten
    along with this atrocity, and the criminals responsible will be emboldened to
    go even further. This will be a radicalizing moment for many if the story is
    allowed to be told.
